# Balance Board Controller

Read `AGENTS.md` first, then `docs/CODEMAP.md` for file locations.

## Stack

- .NET 8, WPF, Windows x64 only
- `BalanceBoard.App` (UI) → `BalanceBoard.Core` (logic)
- Native: `libs/x64/` WiimoteLib + vJoy DLLs

## Rules

- Device/vJoy/input logic stays in Core; UI only binds to `BalanceBoardSession`
- Use `ActionPresets` for profiles; do not duplicate binding logic in UI
- vJoy: always relinquish on shutdown; run `FeederProcessCleanup` before acquire
- Settings: `%AppData%\BalanceBoardApp\settings.json` via `SettingsStore`
- `MainWindow`: respect `_uiReady` and `_suppressSettingEvents`
- Minimal diffs; match file-scoped namespaces and existing patterns
- Never commit logs, baseline/, reference/, or user AppData files

## Verify

```powershell
dotnet build BalanceBoard.sln -c Release
```
